review_data: Reviewed in the United States on April 18, 2020
name: MMorris
title: One of Fage’s best but beware online ordering
review: This is difficult to find these days, so I’m happy that Fresh had it in stock.The cherries are tart and sweet - really tasty!Plus, you get the protein and thick yet creamy texture of Greek yogurt.My two favorites are the tart cherry and Sicilian lemon (only I can never get enough of the lemon- need more in the cup).Update: This is the second time I ordered the product from Whole Foods via Amazon and that I got the BLACK cherry flavor.It’s not at all the same.I love the tartness of the regular cherry flavor (as in the product photo).Black cherry is sweeter.It’s not bad, but if you’re wanting the red cherry, you will be disappointed in this one.
